00087     RMLPositionInputParameters(const unsigned int DegreesOfFreedom) : RMLInputParameters(DegreesOfFreedom)
00088     {
00089         this->MaxVelocityVector                 =   new RMLDoubleVector (DegreesOfFreedom)  ;
00090         this->TargetPositionVector              =   new RMLDoubleVector (DegreesOfFreedom)  ;
00091         this->AlternativeTargetVelocityVector   =   new RMLDoubleVector (DegreesOfFreedom)  ;
00092         
00093         memset(this->MaxVelocityVector->VecData                 ,   0x0 ,       DegreesOfFreedom * sizeof(double));
00094         memset(this->TargetPositionVector->VecData              ,   0x0 ,       DegreesOfFreedom * sizeof(double));
00095         memset(this->AlternativeTargetVelocityVector->VecData   ,   0x0 ,       DegreesOfFreedom * sizeof(double));
00096     }

00770 //  ---------------------- Doxygen info ----------------------
00832 //  ----------------------------------------------------------
00833     bool CheckForValidity(      unsigned int    *DegreeOfFreedom    = NULL
00834                             ,   int             *ErrorCode          = NULL) const
00835     {
00836         unsigned int        i                           =   0;
00837     
00838         double              MinimumOrderOfMagnitude     =   0.0
00839                         ,   MaximumOrderOfMagnitude     =   0.0;
00840                         
00841         for (i = 0; i < this->NumberOfDOFs; i++)
00842         {
00843             if ((this->SelectionVector->VecData)[i])
00844             {
00845                 if (this->MaxVelocityVector->VecData[i] <=  0.0)
00846                 {
00847                     if ((ErrorCode != NULL) && (DegreeOfFreedom != NULL))
00848                     {
00849                         *DegreeOfFreedom    =   i;
00850                         *ErrorCode          =   RMLInputParameters::IP_MAX_VELOCITY;
00851                     }
00852                     return(false);
00853                 }
00854                 if (this->MaxAccelerationVector->VecData[i] <=  0.0)
00855                 {
00856                     if ((ErrorCode != NULL) && (DegreeOfFreedom != NULL))
00857                     {
00858                         *DegreeOfFreedom    =   i;
00859                         *ErrorCode          =   RMLInputParameters::IP_MAX_ACCELERATION;
00860                     }
00861                     return(false);
00862                 }
00863                 if (this->MaxJerkVector->VecData[i] <=  0.0)
00864                 {
00865                     if ((ErrorCode != NULL) && (DegreeOfFreedom != NULL))
00866                     {
00867                         *DegreeOfFreedom    =   i;
00868                         *ErrorCode          =   RMLInputParameters::IP_MAX_JERK;
00869                     }
00870                     return(false);
00871                 }
00872                 if (    fabs(this->TargetVelocityVector->VecData    [i] )
00873                       > (this->MaxVelocityVector->VecData)          [i] )
00874                 {
00875                     if ((ErrorCode != NULL) && (DegreeOfFreedom != NULL))
00876                     {
00877                         *DegreeOfFreedom    =   i;
00878                         *ErrorCode          =   RMLInputParameters::IP_TARGET_VELOCITY;
00879                     }
00880                     return(false);
00881                 }                                               
00882  
00883                 if (    ((this->MaxVelocityVector->VecData)[i]  >=  (this->MaxAccelerationVector->VecData)          [i] )
00884                     &&  ((this->MaxVelocityVector->VecData)[i]  >=  (this->MaxJerkVector->VecData)                  [i] )
00885                     &&  ((this->MaxVelocityVector->VecData)[i]  >=  fabs((this->CurrentPositionVector->VecData)     [i]))
00886                     &&  ((this->MaxVelocityVector->VecData)[i]  >=  fabs((this->TargetPositionVector->VecData)      [i]))
00887                     &&  ((this->MaxVelocityVector->VecData)[i]  >=  fabs((this->CurrentVelocityVector->VecData)     [i]))
00888                     &&  ((this->MaxVelocityVector->VecData)[i]  >=  fabs((this->CurrentAccelerationVector->VecData) [i])))
00889                 {
00890                     MaximumOrderOfMagnitude =   (this->MaxVelocityVector->VecData)[i];
00891                 }
00892                 else
00893                 {
00894                     if (    ((this->MaxAccelerationVector->VecData)[i]  >=  (this->MaxJerkVector->VecData)                  [i] )
00895                         &&  ((this->MaxAccelerationVector->VecData)[i]  >=  fabs((this->CurrentPositionVector->VecData)     [i]))
00896                         &&  ((this->MaxAccelerationVector->VecData)[i]  >=  fabs((this->TargetPositionVector->VecData)      [i]))
00897                         &&  ((this->MaxAccelerationVector->VecData)[i]  >=  fabs((this->CurrentVelocityVector->VecData)     [i]))
00898                         &&  ((this->MaxAccelerationVector->VecData)[i]  >=  fabs((this->CurrentAccelerationVector->VecData) [i])))              
00899                     {
00900                         MaximumOrderOfMagnitude =   (this->MaxAccelerationVector->VecData)[i];
00901                     }
00902                     else
00903                     {
00904                         if (    ((this->MaxJerkVector->VecData)[i]  >=  fabs((this->CurrentPositionVector->VecData)     [i]))
00905                             &&  ((this->MaxJerkVector->VecData)[i]  >=  fabs((this->TargetPositionVector->VecData)      [i]))
00906                             &&  ((this->MaxJerkVector->VecData)[i]  >=  fabs((this->CurrentVelocityVector->VecData)     [i]))
00907                             &&  ((this->MaxJerkVector->VecData)[i]  >=  fabs((this->CurrentAccelerationVector->VecData) [i])))              
00908                         {
00909                             MaximumOrderOfMagnitude =   (this->MaxJerkVector->VecData)[i];
00910                         }
00911                         else
00912                         {
00913                             if (    (fabs((this->CurrentPositionVector->VecData)[i])    >=  fabs((this->TargetPositionVector->VecData)      [i]))
00914                                 &&  (fabs((this->CurrentPositionVector->VecData)[i])    >=  fabs((this->CurrentVelocityVector->VecData)     [i]))
00915                                 &&  (fabs((this->CurrentPositionVector->VecData)[i])    >=  fabs((this->CurrentAccelerationVector->VecData) [i])))              
00916                             {
00917                                 MaximumOrderOfMagnitude =   fabs((this->CurrentPositionVector->VecData)[i]);
00918                             }
00919                             else
00920                             {
00921                                 if (    (fabs((this->TargetPositionVector->VecData)[i]) >=  fabs((this->CurrentVelocityVector->VecData)     [i]))
00922                                     &&  (fabs((this->TargetPositionVector->VecData)[i]) >=  fabs((this->CurrentAccelerationVector->VecData) [i])))              
00923                                 {
00924                                     MaximumOrderOfMagnitude =   fabs((this->TargetPositionVector->VecData)[i]);
00925                                 }
00926                                 else
00927                                 {
00928                                     MaximumOrderOfMagnitude =   fabs((this->CurrentAccelerationVector->VecData)[i]);
00929                                 }
00930                             }
00931                         }       
00932                     }
00933                 }
00934                 
00935                 if (    ((this->MaxVelocityVector->VecData)[i]  <=  (this->MaxAccelerationVector->VecData)  [i] )
00936                     &&  ((this->MaxVelocityVector->VecData)[i]  <=  (this->MaxJerkVector->VecData)          [i] ))
00937                 {
00938                     MinimumOrderOfMagnitude =   (this->MaxVelocityVector->VecData)[i];
00939                 }
00940                 else
00941                 {
00942                     if ((this->MaxAccelerationVector->VecData)[i]   <=  (this->MaxJerkVector->VecData)[i])
00943                     {
00944                         MinimumOrderOfMagnitude =   (this->MaxAccelerationVector->VecData)[i];
00945                     }
00946                     else
00947                     {
00948                         MinimumOrderOfMagnitude =   (this->MaxJerkVector->VecData)[i];
00949                     }               
00950                 }
00951 
00952                 // The target velocity value does not have to be checked as we
00953                 // already know that is lesser than the maximum velocity value.
00954                 // The alternative target velocity vector does not have to be
00955                 // checked.
00956                 
00957                 // The value of MinimumOrderOfMagnitude is greater than
00958                 // zero:                
00959                 if (    (MaximumOrderOfMagnitude / MinimumOrderOfMagnitude)
00960                     >   (double)pow((float)10, (int)(RMLPositionInputParameters::MAXIMUM_MAGNITUDE_RANGE)))
00961                 {
00962                     if ((ErrorCode != NULL) && (DegreeOfFreedom != NULL))
00963                     {
00964                         *DegreeOfFreedom    =   i;
00965                         *ErrorCode          =   RMLInputParameters::IP_ORDER_OF_MAGNITUDE;
00966                     }        
00967                     return(false);
00968                 }
00969             }
00970         }
00971 
00972         if (this->MinimumSynchronizationTime > 1e10)
00973         {
00974             if (ErrorCode != NULL)
00975             {
00976                 *ErrorCode = RMLInputParameters::IP_MINIMUM_SYNC_TIME;
00977             }        
00978             return(false);
00979         }
00980         
00981         if (    (this->OverrideValue < 0.0)
00982             ||  (this->OverrideValue > 100.0)   )
00983         {
00984             if (ErrorCode != NULL)
00985             {
00986                 *ErrorCode = RMLInputParameters::IP_OVERRIDE_VALUE;
00987             }        
00988             return(false);
00989         }
00990 
00991         if (ErrorCode != NULL)
00992         {
00993             *ErrorCode = RMLInputParameters::IP_NO_ERROR;
00994         }
00995 
00996         return(true);
00997     }

01009     void Echo(FILE* FileHandler = stdout) const
01010     {
01011         unsigned int        i   =   0;
01012         
01013         if (FileHandler == NULL)
01014         {
01015             return;
01016         }
01017         
01018         RMLInputParameters::Echo(FileHandler);      
01019         
01020         fprintf(FileHandler, "Max. velocity vector       : ");
01021         for (i = 0; i < this->NumberOfDOFs; i++)
01022         {
01023             fprintf(FileHandler, " %.20le ", this->MaxVelocityVector->VecData[i]);
01024         }
01025         fprintf(FileHandler,   "\nTarget position vector     : ");
01026         for (i = 0; i < this->NumberOfDOFs; i++)
01027         {
01028             fprintf(FileHandler, " %.20le ", this->TargetPositionVector->VecData[i]);
01029         }
01030         fprintf(FileHandler,   "\nAlternative trgt vel. vector: ");
01031         for (i = 0; i < this->NumberOfDOFs; i++)
01032         {
01033             fprintf(FileHandler, " %.20le ", this->AlternativeTargetVelocityVector->VecData[i]);
01034         }       
01035         fprintf(FileHandler, "\n"); 
01036             
01037 
01038         return;
01039     }
